I'm going to ride the cowboy camp.

10:11.520 --> 10:13.663
Ride the cowboy camp.

10:13.683 --> 10:15.546
Ride the cowboy camp.

10:15.806 --> 10:18.490
Ride on the golden range up in the sky.

10:18.510 --> 10:21.555
Up in the sky, way up in the sky.

10:21.655 --> 10:23.718
Yes, we'll ride the cowboy camp.

10:23.738 --> 10:25.981
Yes, sir, way up in the sky.

10:26.041 --> 10:30.248
Brother Buffalo Bell and Sister Lou is going to beat our brother like me and you.

10:30.328 --> 10:33.893
And old Miss Carson, he will too, way up in the sky.

10:36.202 --> 10:43.516
